{"id": "1217317809109995611", "channel_id": "1217317809109995611", "type": 0, "author_id": "1184375279389515849", "author_name": "hazel02661", "author_bot": false, "content": "不知道是bug还是我算错了orz\n\n计算公式应该是（基础+245x吞噬+力量x（吞噬x2+3））x 其他。这样的话我535力量吞噬7次应该是（324+245x7+535x17）=11134，和显示的10154相差980，而980/245=4，所以公式里的245x7实际计算上是245x3，也就是这里之前大招释放次数。\n也就是说吞噬效果里显示的“伤害提高245点”和“力量倍率提高2倍”是不一样的计算方式吗？看起来无限吞噬对前者并没有任何作用…\n\nps.图1是红夫人大招前力量510，红夫人五次伤害+25后力量应该是535；图2是面板显示伤害\nps.如果是我计算错误当我没说orz", "timestamp": "2024-03-13T03:46:22.363000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-03-13T03:49:00.638000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1217317809802186793", "filename": "IMG_0408.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 2380752, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1217317809109995611/1217317809802186793/IMG_0408.png?ex=6a00a84e&is=69ff56ce&hm=4f5a4354a85a0d6758861de9792ce9d9fdbe05607881793dfef6b806eccd6ad4&"}, {"id": "1217317810468945920", "filename": "IMG_0409.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1474333, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1217317809109995611/1217317810468945920/IMG_0409.png?ex=6a00a84e&is=69ff56ce&hm=47d75e3c503b89ea8edc70c272473b038b190b194e5eb3ec140f1599705a71ca&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1217317809109995611", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」尤乌哈希伤害计算问题", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
